flight 
nasa set nov 9 as atlantis launch date but on oct 31 the air 
force delayed the mission because of undisclosed trouble with the 
spy satellite 
nasa plans to launch columbia two to three weeks after atlantis 
flight that will enable the space agency to close the year with 
six shuttle flights three fewer than planned 
