senate republican conference from sen john chafee when the gop 
holds its organizational meeting 
chafee who for the past six years has held the thirdranking 
senate republican post under minority leader bob dole of kansas and 
whip alan simpson of wyoming has angered conservatives with a 
moderate to liberal voting record said bob billings executive 
director of the american conservative union 
when it comes down to conservative causes were about left 
with sen jesse helms billings said in a telephone interview 
monday 
