whether that ad deserves the credit or not tourism officials 
say business is on the upswing again after a sharp drop following 
the oil spill in march 1989 
tourism is alaskas thirdbiggest industry behind oil and 
fishing last summer 560000 visitors spent more than 300 million 
in alaska state officials say 
tourism fell off following the oil spill when pictures of 
blackened beaches and dead sea otters were televised worldwide the 
