tie me up tie me down will carry the new 
nc17 rating when it is released by rcacolumbia pictures home 
video on dec 12 
the provocative comedy by spanish filmmaker pedro almodovar was 
given an x rating by the ratings board of the motion picture 
association of america when it was released theatrically earlier 
