most theaters refused to show movies with x ratings regardless 
of artistic merits because they were associated with hardcore 
pornography 
vidmarks the cook the thief his wife amp her lover was the 
first video to be released with the new rating when it hit stores 
on oct 17 it had been slated for an rrated version and an 
unrated version 
tie me up tie me down almodovars seventh film tells the 
story of a former mental patient who kidnaps a pornographic film 
star and exaddict who eventually falls in love with him 
his women on the verge of a nervous breakdown has grossed 
